Said that she fears for Patricia because she has been at the GH for about two years as a private placement and her parents don't want her. Patricia has no one to speak out for her. Her father who is a police officer comes once in a while to visit. However as a treatment facility the GH is suppose to work with the parents get the children better so they can return home. Instead this is not the case with Patricia. She knows the history and the GH is just housing her there.
